{"tid":2215530,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"周浩鼎再開火反批裁判官整體質素有問題 梁家傑：周是馬道立聲明針對對象","createTime":"2020-09-24T05:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T05:20:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"661de463ee24c8f7269395ed66efff4f688aa8a8","tid":2215530,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:08:34.000Z","msg":"明年初退休的終審法院首席法官馬道立，昨罕有地發表14頁聲明強調司法機構絕不應被政治化，又強調量刑是法院專有職能，由法院獨立行使。主張設量刑委員會的民建聯周浩鼎今日向馬道立開火，指馬的聲明未能釋除「公眾」對司法機構行事失去公正、行事偏頗的質疑。公民黨主席梁家傑則認為，周浩鼎正是馬道立聲明針對的對象之一。<br />\n<br />\n周浩鼎今日港台訪問時聲稱，「我喺（馬道立）聲明睇唔到司法機構會採取乜嘢措施，去有效咁確保下級法院法官或者裁判官，能夠正確咁去運用法律原則」。周批評司法機構讓人感覺「政治化」，是因為在一連串「黑暴」案件中，無論判決、量刑都出現「錯誤運用法律原則、行事不公」情況，自稱對司法機構的批評都是「有理可據」。經常反對香港實施西方民主制度的周浩鼎，引述多個西方國家做法，指英、美國都有設立「量刑委員會」，原因是法院判決受民眾質疑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/WYKFGGGFEBAWTGMUUZO37YKCWY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FWYKFGGGFEBAWTGMUUZO37YKCWY%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFJbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=b6fab0c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FWYKFGGGFEBAWTGMUUZO37YKCWY%2F&h=897016df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/WYKFGGGFEBAWTGMUUZO37YKCWY/</a>"},{"pid":"4b1aaf14281ec4f2cafb99f4eca23f517589adcd","tid":2215530,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:11:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7cb93082a35b7f5bbfdcedbc5d72344af370d6","tid":2215530,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:16:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1ea6712da124af739a4077e931889c13a6ee5e6c","tid":2215530,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:18:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">周浩鼎今日港台訪問時聲稱，「我喺（馬道立）聲明睇唔到司法機構會採取乜嘢措施，去有效咁確保下級法院法官或者裁判官，能夠正確咁去運用法律原則」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好同意，d官放生哂d狗同藍屍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83db415bbb4723c64ba1022cce95e849eb2209ba","tid":2215530,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb7cb93082a35b7f5bbfdcedbc5d72344af370d6","tid":2215530,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:16:55.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54fe616794ca3f5049b89c812b3d7dfdba3d7790","tid":2215530,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ea6712da124af739a4077e931889c13a6ee5e6c","tid":2215530,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:18:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">周浩鼎今日港台訪問時聲稱，「我喺（馬道立）聲明睇唔到司法機構會採取乜嘢措施，去有效咁確保下級法院法官或者裁判官，能夠正確咁去運用法律原則」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好同意，d官放生哂d狗同藍屍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:20:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}